data.description: Offers welcomed! Seller concession of $3,250.00 for buyer's closing costs! Brand new roof put in November of 2023! A must-see charming and maintenance-free 2 story home nestled in the highly sought after of Forest Creek, an esteemed Neal Homes Community! This beautiful home welcomes you with a nice foyer that leads into a cozy living or formal dining room upon entry. The elegant arched hallway offers character! Fantastic open floor plan with ample great room and bar height peninsula in the gorgeous long galley kitchen that features stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, beautiful stiletto tile backsplash and solid wood cabinets with crown molding! Enjoy plenty of natural lighting with volume ceilings, 8-feet double sliding doors and 8-foot glass exterior door. Great layout for entertaining with all the bedrooms upstairs! Impact window by the stairs! Nice double door entry to large master bedroom that features a tray ceiling, walk-in closet and master bathroom with double sink and walk-in shower! Dual climate control for 1st & 2nd floor! The first floor has been freshly painted! Enjoy a spectacular screened patio with an outdoor kitchen featuring a range, built in BBQ, stainless steel sink, exhaust vent and refrigerator all covered with a beautiful Pergola! Plenty of parking with open spots in front as well as a detached 2 car garage that features plenty of wide shelves ideal for storage! Get ready to be fully captivated by the amazing secured gated community of Forest Creek featuring nature trails with a design that preserves the natural beauty found in Parrish! This townhome is conveniently located across the street from the scenic 18-acre lake in which you can enjoy aquatic adventures such as canoe or kayak trip! Relax and enjoy the peaceful view by the gorgeous pier and cazebo! Also withing walking distance, enjoy the central hub of resident activity in the community club house.  Included are an Olympic size lap pool, the hot tub/spa, and a well-equipped fitness center. There is also a meeting center, with a separate resident lounge area with bar, small mini-kitchen area, TV and pool table. Also included in this delightful community are a nearby large playground, fully dedicated doggy park divided for your small and large furry babies! Location! Location! Location! Centrally located close to North River Ranch and just minutes from Fort Hamer bridge which takes you right into Lakewood Ranch! Approximately 30 minutes away from the popular Anna Maria and Bradenton beaches, Sarasota UTC, St Petersburg, Tampa and the surrounding areas! Easy access to I-75, close to shopping, restaurants and so much more! Hurry this gorgeous home won’t last!
